overview: Vulnerable, naked hunks against the power of suited men, make Submit and Play, a true classic. In the next installment of this series, 2 to 1 is how this Gentleman's Club VIP likes to play his filthy games. The Back Room Boy goes deep into his boss' backdoor after work. The Beef Next Door goes under a suited businessman's complete control. A Blackout at the office is the perfect time for some workplace bonding.
title: Submit and Play Vol. 5
